module.name: Chained
module.description: Completes complex tasks using an automated loop

embeddings.text: Write a Python program that reads a file, performs data processing, and outputs the result.
Set up a local development environment by installing the required software, configuring dependencies, and initializing a project.
Create a presentation by gathering information, organizing content, designing slides, and adding multimedia elements.
Build a website from scratch by designing the layout, coding HTML/CSS, integrating JavaScript functionality, and optimizing for responsiveness.
Prepare a recipe by gathering ingredients, following step-by-step instructions, cooking the dish, and serving it.
Plan a vacation by researching destinations, booking flights and accommodations, creating an itinerary, and packing necessary items.
Assemble a piece of furniture by following the provided instructions, identifying and organizing components, and using the correct tools.
Conduct a scientific experiment by formulating a hypothesis, designing the experimental setup, collecting data, analyzing results, and drawing conclusions.
Perform a software system upgrade by backing up data, disabling services, installing the new version, testing functionality, and enabling services again.
Complete a complex math problem by breaking it down into smaller steps, applying relevant formulas or concepts, and progressively solving each part.
